text: Douglas Reid (23 September 1886 - 21 August 1959) was an Australian cricketer. He played three first-class matches for New South Wales between 1908/09 and 1909/10. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1886 births Category:1959 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
title: Douglas Reid (cricketer)
